title: #FBF - Values in Work + Life
description:
Emily and Kathleen with the help of moderator Dana Kaye, share a closer look at their values, how they come into play in business and partnering, and how their values have evolved over time. If you want to hear more of this conversation, check out Episode 182 - Values and Partnering - Live From Printer Row Lit Fest >>
